Pause() - Method in class control.Action
This method use pause method from BasicPlayer class onto the instance of BasicPlayer in this class and add Exceptions of this.

This method use play method from BasicPlayer class onto the instance of BasicPlayer in this class and add Exceptions of this.
Playlist - Class in entities
Playlist class contains a ArrayList with instance of Song class for simulates a Playlist of songs and different options to apply

Constructs a new instance of Playlist class initializing a ArrayList of Song's instance
Playlist() - Constructor for class entities.Playlist

prevSong() - Method in class entities.Playlist
This method open Song with index k-1 in ArrayList, using method open from BasicPlayer 3.0 class
printTable() - Method in class control.Controller
This method is called when you need refresh JTable with name of Songs in ArrayList
progress(int, long, byte[], Map) - Method in class control.Controller
Override method for implement BasicPlayerListener interface, this method run many times per second to get information of Song while this sounds, for more information, view BasicPlayer 3.0 Javadoc
